      <abstract>The paper presents a method for obtaining an approximate solution in 
quadratures of some types of linear ordinary differential equations of 
the second order with nonconstant coefficients.
A solution is constructed on finite intervals or
in a vicinity of given points. As an example, the hypergeometric Gaussian 
equation and the Bessel equation are considered.</abstract>
      <title>A Method for Approximate Solving in Quadratures Some Linear Ordinary Differential Equations of the Second Order with Nonconstant Coefficients</title>
    </articleInfo>
