      <abstract>In the paper we study certain properties of holomorphic functions oflocal differential operators and linear equations containingfunctions of operators of this type. The properties obtained in the paperallow to extendlinear differential operators and linear differential equations to be studiedup to differential operators and linear differential equations of infiniteorder.</abstract>
      <title>Holomorphic Functions of Local Differential Operators and Differential Equations of Infinite Order</title>
    </articleInfo>
